# ── apps/gestalt (active app) ──────────────────────────────────────────────
apps/gestalt/dist
apps/gestalt/.vite
apps/gestalt/playwright-report
apps/gestalt/test-results
# wasm-pack output (generated by pnpm build:wasm)
